  "title": "Screwball!",
  "description": "Screwball! is an improvised ode to the fast-talkin’ rom coms of yesteryear. Witness escalating hijinx! Fashionable attire! Emotional tippling! All delivered by some of Edmonton's most frenetic and cinema-loving improvisers. As seen at the 2025 Bonfire Festival!",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Cast<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Cast<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Paul Blinov, Quinn Contini, Susan Evans, Matthew Kusmire, Dill Prusko, Kelly Turner<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Cast<br/>",
  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "Screwball! is an improv comedy show where performers use audience suggestions to create a brand-new story in the style of classic screwball comedies. Screwball comedies often have fast-paced dialogue and silly actions.",
